models.items

Interface Item

  • All Superinterfaces:
    java.lang.Comparable<Item>

    public interface Item
extends java.lang.Comparable<Item>
    Immutable, represent a generic, customizable item.

    The getId() is used to compare two Item objects which will allow arrays of Item objects to be sorted by their order of creation.
